p:longhorn_namespace_usage_bytes[$growth_window]), \"namespace\", \"$1\", \"claimnamespace\", \"(.+)\")) * 86400, 1), 0), 1095), \"object_type\", \"Customer Quota\", \"\", \"\"), \"object_name\", \"$1\", \"namespace\", \"(.+)\"))",
